 dh-buildinfo,
 ocaml-nox,
 dh-ocaml (>= 0.9), 
 ocaml-findlib (>= 1.2.4)
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Homepage: http://savonet.sourceforge.net/
Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/pkg-ocaml-maint/packages/ocaml-mm.git
